Just The Fax
An entirely self-contained fax program to send and receive faxes.

Things To Do
Things To Do is created to meet all your task-management needs.

Symbol Selector
Symbol Selector allows you use your Symbol, Wingding, and all the other TrueType fonts on your computer in completely new ways. Use fonts in new sizes, in color, bold, or italic. Copy individual symbols and characters to the Windows Clipboard in Rich Text Format (RTF) or Windows Metafile (WMF) format. Save individual symbols and characters as graphic image files in Windows Metafile (WMF) format, or Windows Bitmap (BMP) format. Paste copied and saved symbols and characters into MS Word and other Windows applications. Print any font set installed on your computer.

Tray Calendar
Tray Calendar will help you to keep notes by day of the month in your system tray.

ItsPersonal!
ItsPersonal is a journal for Windows users. It features an attractive, intuitive interface; an unlimited number of days for entries; the ability to print any or all pages; search and replace capabilities; and a spell checker.

ItsTime!
ItsTime is an easy to use alarm and reminder. Never miss another appointment. It&#039;s Time offers you a pop-up reminder for Windows and features unlimited entries, repeat reminders, sound capabilities, and snooze buttons. It&#039;s Time puts a reminder on the screen at the appointed time. The program can also play a pleasant sound with a reminder, or record your own voice to help get you going.

Page Of Labels for Mailing Labels
Easy to use mailing label software. Ideal for small mailing lists. Create one or more pages of mailing labels. Print all labels or individual labels. Works with all standard mailing labels, including Avery labels.

Page O Labels for File Folders
Page O&#039; Labels for File Folders allows you to create, save and print a single page of file folder labels. You can print individual labels or all of the labels on a page. The program works with most standard file folder labels, including Avery labels.
